/CLAUDE.md` - **Architecture/overview documentation**\n4. `/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-system-design.md` - **Initial design spec**\n\nThese files comprehensively document the `cloche status` command with its flags (`--all`), usage patterns, and output formats."}],"totalDurationMs":29336,"totalTokens":46985,"totalToolUseCount":18,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":583,"cache_read_input_tokens":45686,"output_tokens":716,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":583},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
